MADE
AT
THE
UPPER
TOE
LINE
EXACTLY
DOWN
TO
THE
TAPER
LINE
-
NO
FARTHER
-
ARE
MANY
REASONS
-
WOOD
IS
IN
GOOD
AND
COMMON
SUPPLY
-
IT
LENDS
