DECIDED
TO
SEEK
FURTHER
INSIGHT
INTO
THE
PROBLEMS
FACED
BY
OLDER
WORKERS
-
AND
APPROACHED
THOSE
SEVENTY
YEARS
OF
AGE
OR
OLDER
-
THE
RUBERY
-
OWEN
SCHEME
IS
NOW
IN
ITS
FOURTH
YEAR
-
AND
