-
AND
A
SUBORDINATE
IN
CHAPTER
TWO
HE
GAUGED
THE
NATURE
OF
THE
HEARTS
MOVEMENTS
FROM
THE
DISSECTION
OF
LIVING
ANIMALS
-
SHOWING
HOW
THESE
