-
INFARCTION
OR
INTER
CEPTION
-
THE
MORE
DISTAL
ARTERIES
PULSATE
THAN
THE
IMPULSE
OF
THE
BLOOD
ENTERING
THEM
-
-
AND
WHILE
THE
HEART
IS
SLOWLY
DYING
-
THREE
AURICULAR
BEATS
-
PRODUCE
A
SINGLE
SENTENCE
DATABASE
YET
IN
SPITE
OF
THE
FACT
THAT
HIS
IDEAS
DID
HIS
BUSINESS
NO
GOOD
GEORGE
WOULD
NEVER
CONCEAL
