CANNED
FRUIT
FELL
OFF
SHARPLY
WITH
GRADATION
IN
PURCHASES
OF
CANNED
VEGETABLES
AND
CANNED
TOMATOES
-
ALL
TYPES
OF
HOUSEHOLD
BENEFITED
FROM
THE
IMPROVED
SUPPLIES
AND
LOWER
PRICES
OF
FRESH
FRUIT
COMPARED
WITH
1958
-
BUT
