AT
THE
WIRE
CUTTING
OF
OVER
7000000
SQUARE
FEET
OF
FACTORY
SPACE
BUILT
BY
THE
DEVELOPMENT
CORPORATIONS
-
ABOUT
20
PER
CENT
REPRESENTS
EXTENSIONS
BUILT
AFTER
THE
FIRMS
HAD
BECOME
ESTABLISHED
-
IT
IS
