ISOLATED
FROM
LARGE
VOLUMES
OF
SOLU
TION
BY
COPRECIPITATING
THE
LEAD
WITH
A
STRONTIUM
SULPHATE
-
LEAD
AND
STRONTIUM
FORM
MIXED
CRY
STALS
SO
THAT
THE
MORE
INSOLUBLE
LEAD
SULPHATE
IS
ALMOST
COMPLETELY
RECOVERED
EVEN
IF
PRECIPITATION
OF
