BETA
PARTICLES
IS
ALSO
KEPT
TO
A
MINIMUM
BUT
THE
ACCURACY
AND
PRECISION
OF
WEIGHING
THE
PRECIPITATED
SOURCES
SUFFERS
-
ALL
